  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Four Course Combat</h2></strong> is an <strong><i>unique</i></strong> <i>side platformer</i> that brings <i><strong>food to life</strong></i>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beautiful </h2><i>2D pixel art</i> <strong>graphics</strong>, and <i>awesome</i> <strong>8-bit retro music</strong> make this adventure <strong><i>epic!!!!</i></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489220/extras/d9a490313cb34d525d51cd40dae0c79e.avif?t=1630350119\" width=400 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Minimal dialogue</h2> <i><strong>Action packed </strong></i>game, suitable for all ages.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose between</h2>  <i><strong>4 diverse characters!</strong></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1489220/extras/416b9142232e88f9b13913a0305efbec.avif?t=1630350119\" width=500 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use your</h2> <strong>spoon</strong> to <i><strong>smash or flip</strong></i> enemies, and <strong><i>throw</i> forks </strong>to destroy enemies from a distance.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You will</h2>  face a <i><strong>food boss</strong></i> at the end of every level and battle their <strong><i>ingredients</i></strong> along the way.",
